  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Defense Route</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open battlefields, freely design your ultimate defense strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using free-form map design, you'll place various shaped structures to create your own custom maze layouts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/a3a2494792e025f28020d3900f93faa3.poster.avif?t=1763438348\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/a3a2494792e025f28020d3900f93faa3.webm?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/a3a2494792e025f28020d3900f93faa3.mp4?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Merge Skills for Upgrades</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-battler style: combine three for upgrades and synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the perfect skills across different elemental and ability types, then combine them into powerful synergies for maximum impact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/28f27a2aa355fd5ff89ba2eff4adc3d0.poster.avif?t=1763438348\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/28f27a2aa355fd5ff89ba2eff4adc3d0.webm?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/28f27a2aa355fd5ff89ba2eff4adc3d0.mp4?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hundreds of Building Effects</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Countless structures with unique effects for strategic placement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With hundreds of buildings offering distinct advantages, you'll need to carefully consider optimal positioning to maximize each structure's potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/c0bd6d387757ec853a2b3764addb4ea1.poster.avif?t=1763438348\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/c0bd6d387757ec853a2b3764addb4ea1.webm?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/c0bd6d387757ec853a2b3764addb4ea1.mp4?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every Run Feels Fresh</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelike tower defense for a whole new TD experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring procedurally generated Roguelike levels, every run delivers a completely new experience with different skill builds and construction strategies - you'll be hooked for hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/fdd7f5519962c22beaccca47dc68d7d4.poster.avif?t=1763438348\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/fdd7f5519962c22beaccca47dc68d7d4.webm?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/fdd7f5519962c22beaccca47dc68d7d4.mp4?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Defense Route</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open battlefields, freely design your ultimate defense strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using free-form map design, you'll place various shaped structures to create your own custom maze layouts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/a3a2494792e025f28020d3900f93faa3.poster.avif?t=1763438348\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/a3a2494792e025f28020d3900f93faa3.webm?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/a3a2494792e025f28020d3900f93faa3.mp4?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Merge Skills for Upgrades</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-battler style: combine three for upgrades and synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the perfect skills across different elemental and ability types, then combine them into powerful synergies for maximum impact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/28f27a2aa355fd5ff89ba2eff4adc3d0.poster.avif?t=1763438348\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/28f27a2aa355fd5ff89ba2eff4adc3d0.webm?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/28f27a2aa355fd5ff89ba2eff4adc3d0.mp4?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hundreds of Building Effects</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Countless structures with unique effects for strategic placement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With hundreds of buildings offering distinct advantages, you'll need to carefully consider optimal positioning to maximize each structure's potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/c0bd6d387757ec853a2b3764addb4ea1.poster.avif?t=1763438348\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/c0bd6d387757ec853a2b3764addb4ea1.webm?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/c0bd6d387757ec853a2b3764addb4ea1.mp4?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every Run Feels Fresh</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roguelike tower defense for a whole new TD experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring procedurally generated Roguelike levels, every run delivers a completely new experience with different skill builds and construction strategies - you'll be hooked for hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/fdd7f5519962c22beaccca47dc68d7d4.poster.avif?t=1763438348\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/fdd7f5519962c22beaccca47dc68d7d4.webm?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145320/extras/fdd7f5519962c22beaccca47dc68d7d4.mp4?t=1763438348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
